The paper proposes a novel algorithm for multi-view clustering, which involves machine learning techniques such as self-representation learning, matrix factorization, and Hilbert-Schmidt Independence Criterion. These techniques are commonly used in the fields of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), computer vision (cs.CV), data mining (cs.DM), and multimedia (cs.MM). Therefore, these are the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper.
